[[Translation:Main/en/Cycle signal types]]
Set which type of signal should be cycled through when ctrl-clicking on a ready-built signal. Choose between cycling through all [[Main/en/Signals|signal]] types, just the [[Main/en/Signals#Block signals|block signals]] types or only the [[Main/en/Signals#Path Signals|path signals]] types.

0 = Block signals only
1 = Path signals only
2 = All

See also: [[Main/en/Advanced Settings/Construction#Cycle through signal types|Advanced_Settings/Construction#Cycle_through_signal_types]]